<div class="clearfix"></div>
<div class="page-html">
<p class="nonindent" id="p0043-01-0"><b>Thus in the judgment of the committee, the environmental, economic, and humanitarian risks of climate change indicate a pressing need for substantial actions to limit the magnitude of climate change and to prepare for adapting to its impacts.</b> Undertaking such actions will require making choices in the face of incomplete and imperfect information about the future.</p>
</div>
</div>
