<div class="info-overlay" id="info-overlay">
<div class="info-heading">
<span class="info-heading-title">
      America's Climate Choices
    </span>
<span class="info-heading-static">
      Get This Book
    </span>
<div class="info-close">×</div>
</div>
<div class="info-body">
<div class="info-cover-image">
<a href="https://www.nap.edu/catalog/12781/americas-climate-choices"><img data-original="https://www.nap.edu/cover/12781/450" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAAAXNSR0IArs4c6QAAAARnQU1BAACxjwv8YQUAAAAJcEhZcwAADsQAAA7EAZUrDhsAAAANSURBVBhXYzh8+PB/AAffA0nNPuCLAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC" width="450"/></a>
</div>
<div class="info-buttons">
<a class="button buy-button" href="https://cart.nap.edu/cart/cart.php?list=fs&amp;action=buy%20it&amp;record_id=12781&amp;isbn=0-309-14585-6" id="paperback-button"><span data-icon=""></span>Buy Paperback | $29.95</a>
<a class="button buy-button" href="https://cart.nap.edu/cart/cart.php?list=fs&amp;action=buy%20it&amp;record_id=12781&amp;isbn=0-309-30553-5" id="ebook-button"><span data-icon=""></span>Buy Ebook | $23.99</a>
